data.title: Books
data.meta_description: Are you looking for a good book to read? Are you starting out on your reading journey? Or are you returning to reading after a break and don’t know where to start? Then Coffee, Books and Cake, the book-lovers cosy blog could well be for you. Written by a former Bookseller with over a decade in the industry, this blog contains book reviews, lists of books based on a particular theme, all helping you to choose your next read.
data.text:
What type of reader are you?

I ask this question because all over social media are examples of how people read, how they make their selections and choose the next book they will be reading.

So how are we all doing?

I ask this question, because here in the UK it has been an emotional and strange week.

Coffee, Books and Cake is one year old today!

If you could see me now, please note I am eating a lemon fairy cake, drinking a mug of coffee and feeling very happy!
